Sample Data of the PETLER Pacakge

Source: R/PETLER.R
data_org.Rd

A list of training and validation data for illustrating the use of the PETLER algorithm

data_org

Format

A list with 4 data tables:

TrainSurv

baseline survival data for training (labeled); 1st colum: patient id, 2nd colum: event indicator (1=event, 0=censoring), 3rd colum: event time, 4th colum: follow-up time, 5th colum--: covariates.

ValidSurv

baseline survival data for validation; baseline survival data for training (labeled); 1st colum: patient id, 2nd colum: event indicator (1=event, 0=censoring), 3rd colum: event time, 4th colum: follow-up time, 5th colum--: covariates.

TrainCode

1st colum: patient id, 2nd colum: follow-up time, 3rd colum: time label (month), 4th colum-- : predictors.

ValidCode

1st colum: patient id, 2nd colum: follow-up time, 3rd colum: time label (month), 4th colum-- : predictors.
